               <msContents>
                  <summary>This papyrus contains the upper part of a petition to the defensor of an unknown civitas. Hestiodorus received from his brother Kepion while the latter was still alive a room in his house. Probably because there are now difficulties after Kepion's death concerning this room, Hestiodorus addresses the defensor civitatis.</summary>
